2018 is finally here, I'm soOo ready to see the outcome in this growth of family. I'm able to get things ready for March for our new addition to our family baby Tate. My 7 year old son is ready to see his brother an his brother is ready to see him an so is the rest of the family an friends. I pray for better hugs and kisses better communication an better love being spread cause we all need it. Better income an better words being spoken better influence on our children an people an better actions then violence. I pray for my family an friends to reach & grow an let no troubles come to hard but defend by the most high God of Christ. Hope everyone have a Blessed Happy New Years Day & A good year.
